scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: They will'd me say so, madam.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Pray their graces
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: To come near.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: What can be their business
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: With me, a poor weak woman, fall'n from favour?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I do not like their coming. Now I think on't,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: They should be good men; their affairs as righteous:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: But all hoods make not monks.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Peace to your highness!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Your graces find me here part of a housewife,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I would be all, against the worst may happen.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: What are your pleasures with me, reverend lords?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: May it please you noble madam, to withdraw
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Into your private chamber, we shall give you
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: The full cause of our coming.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Speak it here:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: There's nothing I have done yet, o' my conscience,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Deserves a corner: would all other women
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Could speak this with as free a soul as I do!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: My lords, I care not, so much I am happy
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Above a number, if my actions
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Were tried by every tongue, every eye saw 'em,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Envy and base opinion set against 'em,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I know my life so even. If your business
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Seek me out, and that way I am wife in,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Out with it boldly: truth loves open dealing.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Tanta est erga te mentis integritas, regina
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: serenissima,--
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: O, good my lord, no Latin;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I am not such a truant since my coming,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: As not to know the language I have lived in:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: A strange tongue makes my cause more strange,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: suspicious;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Pray, speak in English: here are some will thank you,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: If you speak truth, for their poor mistress' sake;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Believe me, she has had much wrong: lord cardinal,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: The willing'st sin I ever yet committed
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: May be absolved in English.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Noble lady,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I am sorry my integrity should breed,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And service to his majesty and you,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: So deep suspicion, where all faith was meant.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: We come not by the way of accusation,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: To taint that honour every good tongue blesses,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Nor to betray you any way to sorrow,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: You have too much, good lady; but to know
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: How you stand minded in the weighty difference
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Between the king and you; and to deliver,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Like free and honest men, our just opinions
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And comforts to your cause.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Most honour'd madam,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: My Lord of York, out of his noble nature,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Zeal and obedience he still bore your grace,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Forgetting, like a good man your late censure
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Both of his truth and him, which was too far,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Offers, as I do, in a sign of peace,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: His service and his counsel.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: My lords, I thank you both for your good wills;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Ye speak like honest men; pray God, ye prove so!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: But how to make ye suddenly an answer,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: In such a point of weight, so near mine honour,--
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: More near my life, I fear,--with my weak wit,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And to such men of gravity and learning,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: In truth, I know not. I was set at work
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Among my maids: full little, God knows, looking
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Either for such men or such business.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: For her sake that I have been,--for I feel
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: The last fit of my greatness,--good your graces,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Let me have time and counsel for my cause:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Alas, I am a woman, friendless, hopeless!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Madam, you wrong the king's love with these fears:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Your hopes and friends are infinite.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: In England
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: But little for my profit: can you think, lords,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: That any Englishman dare give me counsel?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Or be a known friend, 'gainst his highness' pleasure,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Though he be grown so desperate to be honest,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And live a subject? Nay, forsooth, my friends,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: They that must weigh out my afflictions,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: They that my trust must grow to, live not here:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: They are, as all my other comforts, far hence
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: In mine own country, lords.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I would your grace
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Would leave your griefs, and take my counsel.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: How, sir?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Put your main cause into the king's protection;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: He's loving and most gracious: 'twill be much
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Both for your honour better and your cause;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: For if the trial of the law o'ertake ye,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: You'll part away disgraced.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: He tells you rightly.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Ye tell me what ye wish for both,--my ruin:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Is this your Christian counsel? out upon ye!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Heaven is above all yet; there sits a judge
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: That no king can corrupt.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Your rage mistakes us.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: The more shame for ye: holy men I thought ye,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Upon my soul, two reverend cardinal virtues;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: But cardinal sins and hollow hearts I fear ye:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Mend 'em, for shame, my lords. Is this your comfort?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: The cordial that ye bring a wretched lady,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: A woman lost among ye, laugh'd at, scorn'd?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I will not wish ye half my miseries;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: I have more charity: but say, I warn'd ye;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Take heed, for heaven's sake, take heed, lest at once
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: The burthen of my sorrows fall upon ye.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Madam, this is a mere distraction;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: You turn the good we offer into envy.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Ye turn me into nothing: woe upon ye
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And all such false professors! would you have me--
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: If you have any justice, any pity;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: If ye be any thing but churchmen's habits--
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Put my sick cause into his hands that hates me?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Alas, has banish'd me his bed already,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: His love, too long ago! I am old, my lords,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And all the fellowship I hold now with him
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Is only my obedience. What can happen
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: To me above this wretchedness? all your studies
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Make me a curse like this.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Your fears are worse.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Have I lived thus long--let me speak myself,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Since virtue finds no friends--a wife, a true one?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: A woman, I dare say without vain-glory,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Never yet branded with suspicion?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Have I with all my full affections
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Still met the king? loved him next heaven?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: obey'd him?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Been, out of fondness, superstitious to him?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Almost forgot my prayers to content him?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And am I thus rewarded? 'tis not well, lords.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Bring me a constant woman to her husband,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: One that ne'er dream'd a joy beyond his pleasure;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: And to that woman, when she has done most,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Yet will I add an honour, a great patience.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Madam, you wander from the good we aim at.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: My lord, I dare not make myself so guilty,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: To give up willingly that noble title
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Your master wed me to: nothing but death
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Shall e'er divorce my dignities.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Pray, hear me.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Would I had never trod this English earth,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE I.  London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.

line_text: Or felt the flatteries that grow upon it!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth

scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: My noble partners, and myself, thus pray:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: All comfort, joy, in this most gracious lady,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Heaven ever laid up to make parents happy,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: May hourly fall upon ye!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Thank you, good lord archbishop:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: What is her name?
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Elizabeth.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Stand up, lord.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: With this kiss take my blessing: God protect thee!
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Into whose hand I give thy life.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Amen.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: My noble gossips, ye have been too prodigal:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: I thank ye heartily; so shall this lady,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: When she has so much English.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Let me speak, sir,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: For heaven now bids me; and the words I utter
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Let none think flattery, for they'll find 'em truth.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: This royal infant--heaven still move about her!--
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Though in her cradle, yet now promises
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Upon this land a thousand thousand blessings,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Which time shall bring to ripeness: she shall be--
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: But few now living can behold that goodness--
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: A pattern to all princes living with her,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And all that shall succeed: Saba was never
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: More covetous of wisdom and fair virtue
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Than this pure soul shall be: all princely graces,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: That mould up such a mighty piece as this is,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: With all the virtues that attend the good,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Shall still be doubled on her: truth shall nurse her,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Holy and heavenly thoughts still counsel her:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: She shall be loved and fear'd: her own shall bless her;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Her foes shake like a field of beaten corn,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And hang their heads with sorrow: good grows with her:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: In her days every man shall eat in safety,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Under his own vine, what he plants; and sing
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: The merry songs of peace to all his neighbours:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: God shall be truly known; and those about her
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: From her shall read the perfect ways of honour,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And by those claim their greatness, not by blood.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Nor shall this peace sleep with her: but as when
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: The bird of wonder dies, the maiden phoenix,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Her ashes new create another heir,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: As great in admiration as herself;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: So shall she leave her blessedness to one,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: When heaven shall call her from this cloud of darkness,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Who from the sacred ashes of her honour
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Shall star-like rise, as great in fame as she was,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And so stand fix'd: peace, plenty, love, truth, terror,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: That were the servants to this chosen infant,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Shall then be his, and like a vine grow to him:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Wherever the bright sun of heaven shall shine,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: His honour and the greatness of his name
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Shall be, and make new nations: he shall flourish,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And, like a mountain cedar, reach his branches
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: To all the plains about him: our children's children
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Shall see this, and bless heaven.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Thou speakest wonders.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: She shall be, to the happiness of England,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: An aged princess; many days shall see her,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And yet no day without a deed to crown it.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Would I had known no more! but she must die,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: She must, the saints must have her; yet a virgin,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: A most unspotted lily shall she pass
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: To the ground, and all the world shall mourn her.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: O lord archbishop,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Thou hast made me now a man! never, before
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: This happy child, did I get any thing:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: This oracle of comfort has so pleased me,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: That when I am in heaven I shall desire
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: To see what this child does, and praise my Maker.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: I thank ye all. To you, my good lord mayor,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And your good brethren, I am much beholding;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: I have received much honour by your presence,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: And ye shall find me thankful. Lead the way, lords:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Ye must all see the queen, and she must thank ye,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: She will be sick else. This day, no man think
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: Has business at his house; for all shall stay:
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: This little one shall make it holiday.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: SCENE V.  The palace.

line_text: 'Tis ten to one this play can never please
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: All that are here: some come to take their ease,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: And sleep an act or two; but those, we fear,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: We have frighted with our trumpets; so, 'tis clear,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: They'll say 'tis naught: others, to hear the city
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: Abused extremely, and to cry 'That's witty!'
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: Which we have not done neither: that, I fear,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: All the expected good we're like to hear
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: For this play at this time, is only in
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: The merciful construction of good women;
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: For such a one we show'd 'em: if they smile,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: And say 'twill do, I know, within a while
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: All the best men are ours; for 'tis ill hap,
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE

line_text: If they hold when their ladies bid 'em clap.
play_title_long: The Famous History of the Life of Henry the Eighth
scene_title: EPILOGUE
